"https://www.netflix.com/th/title/81739747","overview":"ในกรุงเทพฯ ช่วงปี 1980 โจรเจ้าเล่ห์ก่อเหตุปล้นอุกอาจหลายครั้ง โดยสร้างความฉงนงงงวยให้ทั้งเจ้าหน้าที่และประชาชน จนกระทั่งตำรวจนายหนึ่งหมายมั่นที่จะจับโจรรายนี้ให้ได้"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":117,"tagline":"Meet the \"King of Thieves\", whose life is coming to an end.","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/title/81739747","overview":"In 1980s Bangkok, a wily thief stages a series of daring heists, baffling the authorities and the public — until one cop sets out to take him down."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Nascido para o Mal","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/br/title/81739747","overview":"Na Bangkok da década de 1980, um ladrão astuto comete uma série de assaltos ousados, impressionando as autoridades e o público. Até que um policial decide ir atrás dele."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"悍匪传奇","runtime":117,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在 20 世纪 80 年代的曼谷，狡猾的窃匪犯下一连串大胆劫案，令当局和公众感到无所适从，于是一名警察决心将其捉拿归案。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Nacido para el crimen","runtime":0,"tagline":"Conozcan al \"Rey de los Ladrones\", cuya vida está llegando a su fin.","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/es/title/81739747","overview":"Bangkok, década de 1980. Un astuto ladrón que da golpes audaces deja perplejos al público y las autoridades... hasta que un policía se propone atraparlo."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Tính bản ác","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/vn/title/81739747","overview":"Những năm 1980 ở Bangkok, một tên trộm xảo quyệt thực hiện hàng loạt vụ trộm táo bạo, khiến chính quyền và công chúng hoang mang – cho đến khi một cảnh sát quyết tâm hạ bệ hắn."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"띠야이: 본 투 비 배드","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/kr/title/81739747","overview":"1980년대 방콕, 교활한 도둑이 대담한 범행을 연달아 벌이며 경찰과 대중을 혼란에 빠뜨린다. 그리고 마침내 한 형사가 그를 잡기 위해 나선다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Książę złodziei","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pl/title/81739747","overview":"Bangkok, lata 80. XX w. Sprytny złodziej dokonuje serii zuchwałych napadów, wprawiając w zdumienie władze i społeczeństwo — aż pewien glina postanawia dać mu nauczkę."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"שעתו היפה של טי יאי","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/il/title/81739747","overview":"בנגקוק, שנות השמונים. גנב ערמומי מוציא לפועל שורה של מקרי שוד נועזים ומבלבל את הרשויות ואת הציבור – עד ששוטר אחד מחליט להפיל אותו."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fr/title/81739747","overview":"Bangkok, années 80. Un voleur ingénieux orchestre une série de cambriolages audacieux qui déconcertent les autorités et le public, jusqu'à ce qu'un flic se jure de le coffrer."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Născut să fii rău","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ro/title/81739747","overview":"În Bangkokul anilor ’80, un hoț șiret pune la cale o serie de jafuri îndrăznețe, uluind autoritățile și publicul, până când un polițist își propune să-l prindă."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Nacido para el crimen","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/mx/title/81739747","overview":"Bangkok, años 80. Un astuto ladrón realiza una serie de robos audaces que desconciertan a todos..., hasta que un policía se decide a detenerlo."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"تي ياي: وُلدَ ليكون سيئًا","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sa/title/81739747","overview":"في \"بانكوك\" خلال الثمانينيات، ينفّذ لص ماكر سلسلة من عمليات السرقة الجريئة، مما يحيّر السلطات والشعب... إلى أن يعتزم شرطي القبض عليه."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"悍匪傳奇","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/81739747","overview":"1980 年代曼谷，一名狡猾的小偷犯下一連串重大竊案，警民雙方都毫無頭緒，幸好一位警察不畏艱難，決心將他繩之以法。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"تي ياي: وُلدَ ليكون سيئًا","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ae/title/81739747","overview":"في \"بانكوك\" خلال الثمانينيات، ينفّذ لص ماكر سلسلة من عمليات السرقة الجريئة، مما يحيّر السلطات والشعب... إلى أن يعتزم شرطي القبض عليه."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/de/title/81739747","overview":"Bangkok, 1980er: Ein gerissener Dieb inszeniert gewagte Raubüberfälle und verblüfft so die Behörden und die Öffentlichkeit, bis ihm ein Polizist auf die Schliche kommt."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"悍匪传奇","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sg-zh/title/81739747","overview":"在 20 世纪 80 年代的曼谷，狡猾的窃匪犯下一连串大胆劫案，令当局和公众感到无所适从，于是一名警察决心将其捉拿归案。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Rođeni zlikovac","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hr/title/81739747","overview":"1980-ih u Bangkoku prepredeni lopov izvede niz odvažnih pljački, zbunjujući policiju i javnost... sve dok mu jedan policajac ne odluči stati na kraj."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Zrozen ke zločinu","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/cz/title/81739747","overview":"V 80. letech zamotá policii i obyvatelům Bangkoku hlavu série rafinovaných loupeží. Jeden z vyšetřovatelů se ale rozhodne dopadnout pachatele za každou cenu."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/dk/title/81739747","overview":"I 1980'ernes Bangkok iscenesætter en snedig tyv en række dristige røverier, der forvirrer myndighederne og offentligheden – indtil en betjent sætter sig for at fange ham."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"悍匪傳奇","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tw/title/81739747","overview":"1980 年代曼谷，一名狡猾的小偷犯下一連串重大竊案，警民雙方都毫無頭緒，幸好一位警察不畏艱難，決心將他繩之以法。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Γεννημένος Κλέφτης","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/gr/title/81739747","overview":"Στην Μπανγκόκ του '80, ένας κλέφτης κάνει μια σειρά από τολμηρές ληστείες, μπερδεύοντας τις αρχές και τον κόσμο — μέχρι που ένας αστυνομικός αποφασίζει να τον συλλάβει."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fi/title/81739747","overview":"Ovela varas suorittaa uskaliaita ryöstöjä 1980-luvun Bangkokissa, eivätkä viranomaiset voi hänelle mitään – kunnes yksi poliisi ottaa asian omakseen."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/in-hi/title/81739747","overview":""},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/nl/title/81739747","overview":"In het Bangkok van de jaren 80 zet een slimme dief een reeks overvallen op, tot verbijstering van de autoriteiten en het publiek. Tot een agent besluit hem te stoppen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai : Le crime dans le sang","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ca-fr/title/81739747","overview":"À Bangkok dans les années 1980, un voleur rusé élabore une série de cambriolages, mystifiant les autorités et le public, jusqu'à ce qu'un policier se mette sur sa piste."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/my/title/81739747","overview":"Bangkok, 1980-an. Seorang pencuri licik membuat rompakan berani yang mengejutkan pihak berkuasa dan orang ramai. Seorang pegawai polis bertekad untuk menumpaskannya."},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"Született rosszfiú","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hu/title/81739747","overview":"Az 1980-as évek Bangkokjában egy ravasz tolvaj kitervel egy merész rablássorozatot, amivel a hatóságokat és a nyilvánosságot is összezavarja — egyetlen rendőr kivételével."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/it/title/81739747","overview":"Nella Bangkok degli anni '80, un astuto ladro compie una serie di audaci rapine, lasciando sgomenti le autorità e i cittadini... finché un poliziotto non decide di catturarlo."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"ティーヤイ: ボーン・トゥ・ビー・バッド","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/jp/title/81739747","overview":"1980年代のバンコクで、世間を翻弄する狡猾な強盗犯がいた。捜査を巧みにかく乱し、大胆不敵な犯行を繰り返すその男を捕らえるため、ひとりの警察官が立ち上がる。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/id/title/81739747","overview":"Di Bangkok tahun 1980-an, pencuri cerdik menyusun serangkaian perampokan berani, mengejutkan pihak berwenang dan publik—hingga seorang polisi bersiap untuk menangkapnya."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/se/title/81739747","overview":"I 1980-talets Bangkok härjar en slug tjuv som förbryllar myndigheterna och allmänheten – tills en polis bestämmer sig för att få fast honom."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Nascido Para Ser Mau","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pt/title/81739747","overview":"Nos anos 90 em Banguecoque, um ladrão astuto faz uma série de assaltos ousados, confundindo as autoridades e o público, até que aparece um polícia determinado a detê-lo."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/no/title/81739747","overview":"En slu tyv gjennomfører en rekke dristige ran som forvirrer myndighetene og offentligheten i Bangkok på 1980-tallet – inntil en politimann bestemmer seg for å ta ham."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Ти Яй: Рожденный быть плохим","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ru/title/81739747","overview":"В Бангкоке 1980-х хитрый вор совершает серию дерзких ограблений, бросая вызов властям. Остановить его может лишь один полицейский."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Kötülük İçin Doğanlar","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tr/title/81739747","overview":"1980'lerde, Bangkok'ta kurnaz bir hırsız, bir dizi cüretkâr soygun gerçekleştirerek emniyet güçlerini ve halkı şaşkına çevirir. Ta ki bir polis, onu yakalamaya ant içene dek."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Tee Yai: Born to Be Bad","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ph/title/81739747","overview":"Sa 1980s Bangkok, may series ng daring heists ang isang magnanakaw na nagpawindang sa mga awtoridad at publiko—hanggang sa nagdesisyon ang isang pulis na patumbahin siya."},"name":"","iso_639_1":"tl","iso_3166_1":"PH","english_name":"Tagalog"},{"data":{"title":"Народжений бути поганцем","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ua/title/81739747","overview":"Бангкок, 1980-ті. Хитрий злодій влаштовує серію зухвалих пограбувань, заганяючи в глухий кут владу й громадськість, але один детектив рішуче налаштований спіймати його."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[],"similar_content":[],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt35669044","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":105746,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AD","r